---
// SCENE 11 — the final frame. The buildup footage carries the close.
---

<section class="section cta">
  <div class="media-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <video
      class="kb"
      src="/media/hero/buildup.mp4"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      poster="/media/hero/soul_v2b.jpg"
      data-anim
      aria-hidden="true"></video>
    <div class="scrim"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container inner">
    <p class="slug reveal reveal-sm"><span class="no">Scene 10</span> The final frame</p>
    <h2 class="reveal">Give your agent a memory <em>that survives.</em></h2>
    <p class="sub reveal">
      Project memory belongs in the repository, where it ships with the code, shows up in diffs, and
      is reviewed alongside changes. As tool calls the agent can't forget to make, not advice it has
      to remember.
    </p>
    <button class="cmd big reveal" type="button" data-copy="uvx --from clauderizer clauderize init">
      <code><span class="prompt">$</span> uvx --from clauderizer clauderize init</code>
      <span class="copy-hint">copy</span>
    </button>
    <div class="row reveal">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/collincusce/Clauderizer">Star on GitHub</a
      >
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://pypi.org/project/clauderizer/">View on PyPI</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--ink-950);
    overflow: clip;
    min-height: 52svh;
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .media-bg video {
    opacity: 0.55;
  }
  .inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.6rem;
  }
  h2 {
    max-width: 16ch;
  }
  .sub {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 42rem;
  }
  .cmd.big {
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    padding: 1.05rem 1.4rem;
  }
  .cmd.big code {
    font-size: clamp(0.82rem, 2.4vw, 1rem);
  }
  .row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
</style>
